Lama_Sss_ior.00004.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559105&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559105&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220177\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Sss_ior.00004.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220135\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"87d6ca12-d293-4473-b82e-87ac45a1feb8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559105&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559105&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Sss_ior.00005.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00005.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559104&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00005.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559104&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220174\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Sss_ior.00005.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220135\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"04431dd0-e884-41c8-8732-080d038874d0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00005.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559104&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00005.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559104&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Sss_ior.00006.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559104&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559104&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220171\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Sss_ior.00006.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220135\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7c40e0a0-cc42-4506-9906-8fd431135a58\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559104&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_ior.00006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330559104&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-blue3\">IOR examples : 1.0 / 1.2 / 1.3 / 1.4 / 1.5 / 2.0</span><br/><br/></p><p><br/></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"0ed091b6-911e-4807-a6d4-bf9f06000832\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"LamaSSS-ProTip\">Pro Tip</h3><p>The IOR for Skin is approximately 1.4.</p></div></div><p><br/></p><p><strong>Anisotropy</strong></p><p>Light can scatter forward or backwards inside a surface. Using anisotropy, you can cause the light to scatter more strongly forward along the direction of the light ray. This may have the effect of making the object appear more transparent.</p><p>This attribute behaves slightly different with different Albedo Inversion Models. For human skin, a value of 0.7 is recommended when using Pixar's Albedo Inversion Model, and a value of 0.2 is recommended for Chiang Albedo Inversion Model.</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>Bleed (Davis Mode Only)</strong></p><p>This can increase the distance light travels, just like the Radius control. However, this control attempts to maintain the finer details while making light scatter further.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"391edcc7-726e-43a8-92ab-7185fcd33e75\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Sss_blend.00001.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_blend.00001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330558915&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542220135/Lama_Sss_blend.00001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330558915&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542220168\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Sss_blend.00001.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542220135\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"460edf48-1381-4075-95f1-56625ca537b3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_blend.00001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330558915&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542220135/Lama_Sss_blend.00001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330558915&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Sss_blend.00002.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thum